(String.Empty);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine//Function for Decrypting proposeDi2015NewLinestatic string SymmetricDecryption(string str, byte[] key, byte[] IV)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinetryDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine//---converts the encrypted string into a byte array---Di2015NewLinebyte[] b = 9989709Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class CustomComparer : IComparer<string>Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public int Compare(string x, string y)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var regex = new Regex("^(d+)");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // run the regex on both stringsDi2015NewLine        var xRegexResult = regex.Match(x);Di2015NewLine        var yRegexResult = regex.Match(y);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // check if they are both numbersDi2015NewLine        if (xRegexResult.Success && yRegexResult.Success)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return int.Parse(xRegexResult.Groups[1].Value).CompareTo(int.Parse(yRegexResult.Groups[1].Value));Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // otherwise return as string comparisonDi2015NewLine        return x.CompareTo(y);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10002497Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static bool CompileCSharpCode(String sourceFile, String outFile)Di2015NewLine        { Di2015NewLine            // Obtain an ICodeCompiler from a CodeDomProvider class.Di2015NewLine            CSharpCodeProvider provider = new CSharpCodeProvider(); Di2015NewLine            ICodeCompiler compiler = provider.CreateCompiler(); // Build the parameters for source compilation. Di2015NewLine            CompilerParameters cp = new CompilerParameters(); // Add an assembly reference. Di2015NewLine            cp.ReferencedAssemblies.Add("System.dll"); // Generate an class library instead of // a executable. Di2015NewLine            cp.GenerateExecutable = false; // Set the assembly file name to generate. Di2015NewLine            cp.OutputAssembly = outFile; // Save the assembly as a physical file. Di2015NewLine            cp.GenerateInMemory = false; // Invoke compilation. Di2015NewLine            CompilerResults cr = compiler.CompileAssemblyFromFile(cp, sourceFile);Di2015NewLine            if (cr.Errors.Count > 0)Di2015NewLine            { // Display compilation errors. Di2015NewLine                Console.WriteLine("Errors building {0} into {1}", sourceFile, cr.PathToAssembly);Di2015NewLine                foreach (CompilerError ce in cr.Errors)Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    Console.WriteLine(" {0}", ce.ToString());Di2015NewLine                    Console.WriteLine();Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                Console.WriteLine("Source {0} built into {1} successfully.", sourceFile, cr.PathToAssembly);Di2015NewLine            } // Return the results of compilation. Di2015NewLine            if (cr.Errors.Count > 0) { return false; } else { return true; }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine

10003320Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic PropertyInfo GetPropertyInfo<TSource, TProperty>(Di2015NewLine    TSource source,Di2015NewLine    Expression<Func<TSource, TProperty>> propertyLambda)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    Type type = typeof(TSource);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    MemberExpression member = propertyLambda.Body as MemberExpression;Di2015NewLine    if (member == null)Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentException(string.Format(Di2015NewLine            "Expression '{0}' refers to a method, not a property.",Di2015NewLine            propertyLambda.ToString()));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    PropertyInfo propInfo = member.Member as PropertyInfo;Di2015NewLine    if (propInfo == null)Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentException(string.Format(Di2015NewLine            "Expression '{0}' refers to a field, not a property.",Di2015NewLine            propertyLambda.ToString()));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (type != propInfo.ReflectedType &&Di2015NewLine        !type.IsSubclassOf(propInfo.ReflectedType))Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentException(string.Format(Di2015NewLine            "Expresion '{0}' refers to a property that is not from type {1}.",Di2015NewLine            propertyLambda.ToString(),Di2015NewLine            type));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return propInfo;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10018828Di2015UniqueSeparator    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Gets the value of all the fields or properties on an object that are decorated with the specified attributeDi2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    private IEnumerable<object> GetValuesFromAttributedMembers<TAttribute>(object obj)Di2015NewLine        where TAttribute : AttributeDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var values1 = obj.GetType().GetFields()Di2015NewLine                        .Where(fi => fi.GetCustomAttributes(typeof(TAttribute), true).Any())Di2015NewLine                        .Select(fi => fi.GetValue(obj));Di2015NewLine        var values2 = obj.GetType().GetProperties()Di2015NewLine                        .Where(pi => pi.GetCustomAttributes(typeof(TAttribute), true).Any())Di2015NewLine                        .Select(pi => pi.GetValue(obj, null));Di2015NewLine        return values1.Concat(values2);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

10027211Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class BrainTeaser {Di2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// The possible groupings are returned in order of the 'most' desirable first. Equivalent groupings are not returned (e.g. 2 + 1 vs. 1 + 2). Only one representantDi2015NewLine    /// of each grouping is returned (ordered ascending. e.g. 1 + 1 + 2 + 4 + 5)Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="numberOfFriends"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public IEnumerable<PossibleGrouping> Solve(int numberOfFriends) {Di2015NewLine        if (numberOfFriends == 1) {Di2015NewLine            yield return new PossibleGrouping(1);Di2015NewLine            yield break;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        HashSet<PossibleGrouping> possibleGroupings = new HashSet<PossibleGrouping>(new PossibleGroupingComparer());Di2015NewLine        foreach (var grouping in Solve(numberOfFriends - 1)) {Di2015NewLine            // for each group we create 'n+1' new groups Di2015NewLine            // 1 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 Di2015NewLine            // BecomesDi2015NewLine            //      (1+1) + 1 + 2 + 3 + 4  we can add a friend to the first groupDi2015NewLine            //      1 + (1+1) + 2 + 3 + 4  we can add a friend to the second groupDi2015NewLine            //      1 + 1 + (2+1) + 3 + 4  we can add a friend to the third groupDi2015NewLine            //      1 + 1 + 2 + (3+1) + 4  we can add a friend to the forth groupDi2015NewLine            //      1 + 1 + 2 + 3 + (4+1) we can add a friend to the fifth groupDi2015NewLine            //      (1 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 4) + 1  friend has to sit aloneDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            AddAllPartitions(grouping, possibleGroupings);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        foreach (var possibleGrouping in possibleGroupings.OrderByDescending(x => x)) {Di2015NewLine            yield return possibleGrouping;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private void AddAllPartitions(PossibleGrouping grouping, HashSet<PossibleGrouping> possibleGroupings) {Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < grouping.FriendsInGroup.Length; i++) {Di2015NewLine            int[] newFriendsInGroup = (int[]) grouping.FriendsInGroup.Clone();Di2015NewLine            newFriendsInGroup[i] = newFriendsInGroup[i] + 1;Di2015NewLine            possibleGroupings.Add(new PossibleGrouping(newFriendsInGroup));Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        var friendsInGroupWithOneAtTheEnd = grouping.FriendsInGroup.Concat(new[] {1}).ToArray();Di2015NewLine        possibleGroupings.Add(new PossibleGrouping(friendsInGroupWithOneAtTheEnd));Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine/// <summary>Di2015NewLine/// A possible grouping of friends. E.g.Di2015NewLine/// 1 + 1 + 2 + 2 + 4 (10 friends). The array is sorted by the least friends in an group.Di2015NewLine/// </summary>Di2015NewLinepublic class PossibleGrouping : IComparable<PossibleGrouping> {Di2015NewLine    private readonly int[] friendsInGroup;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public int[] FriendsInGroup {Di2015NewLine        get { return friendsInGroup; }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private readonly int sum;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public PossibleGrouping(params int[] friendsInGroup) {Di2015NewLine        this.friendsInGroup = friendsInGroup.OrderBy(x => x).ToArray();Di2015NewLine        sum = friendsInGroup.Sum();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public int Sum {Di2015NewLine        get { return sum; }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// determine which group is more desirable. Example:Di2015NewLine    /// Consider g1: 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 vs g2: 1 + 1 + 2 + 2 + 4  Di2015NewLine    /// Group each sequence by the number of occurrences:Di2015NewLine    /// Di2015NewLine    /// group   | g1   | g2Di2015NewLine    /// --------|-------------Di2015NewLine    /// 1       | 1    | 2Di2015NewLine    /// ----------------------Di2015NewLine    /// 2       | 1    | 2Di2015NewLine    /// ----------------------Di2015NewLine    /// 3       | 1    | 0Di2015NewLine    /// ----------------------Di2015NewLine    /// 4       | 1    | 1Di2015NewLine    /// ----------------------Di2015NewLine    /// Di2015NewLine    /// Sequence 'g1' should score 'higher' because it has 'less' 'ones' (least desirable) elements. Di2015NewLine    /// Di2015NewLine    /// If both sequence would have same number of 'ones', we'd compare the 'twos'.Di2015NewLine    /// Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="other"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public int CompareTo(PossibleGrouping other) {Di2015NewLine        var thisGroup = (from n in friendsInGroup group n by n).ToDictionary(x => x.Key,Di2015NewLine                                                                             x => x.Count());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var otherGroup = (from n in other.friendsInGroup group n by n).ToDictionary(x => x.Key,Di2015NewLine                                                                                    x => x.Count());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return WhichGroupIsBetter(thisGroup, otherGroup);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private int WhichGroupIsBetter(IDictionary<int, int> thisGroup, IDictionary<int, int> otherGroup) {Di2015NewLine        int maxNumberOfFriendsInAGroups = Math.Max(thisGroup.Keys.Max(), otherGroup.Keys.Max());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        for (int numberOfFriendsInGroup = 1;Di2015NewLine             numberOfFriendsInGroup <= maxNumberOfFriendsInAGroups;Di2015NewLine             numberOfFriendsInGroup++) {Di2015NewLine            // zero means that the current grouping does not contain a such group with 'numberOfFriendsInGroup'Di2015NewLine            // in the example above, e.g. group '3'Di2015NewLine            int thisNumberOfGroups = thisGroup.ContainsKey(numberOfFriendsInGroup)Di2015NewLine                                         ? thisGroup[numberOfFriendsInGroup]Di2015NewLine                                         : 0;Di2015NewLine            int otherNumberOfGroups = otherGroup.ContainsKey(numberOfFriendsInGroup)Di2015NewLine                                          ? otherGroup[numberOfFriendsInGroup]Di2015NewLine                                          : 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            int compare = thisNumberOfGroups.CompareTo(otherNumberOfGroups);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            if (compare != 0) {Di2015NewLine                // positive score means that the other group has more occurrences. e.g. 'this' group might have 2 groups with each 2 friends,Di2015NewLine                // but the other solution might have 3 groups with each 2 friends. It's obvious that (because both solutions must sum up to the same value)Di2015NewLine                // this 'solution' must contain a grouping with more than 3 friends which is more desirable.Di2015NewLine                return -compare;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        // they must be 'equal' in this case.Di2015NewLine        return 0;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public override string ToString() {Di2015NewLine        return string.Join("+", friendsInGroup.Select(x => x.ToString()).ToArray());Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic class PossibleGroupingComparer : EqualityComparer<PossibleGrouping> {Di2015NewLine    public override bool Equals(PossibleGrouping x, PossibleGrouping y) {Di2015NewLine        return x.FriendsInGroup.SequenceEqual(y.FriendsInGroup);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// may not be the best hashcode function. for alternatives look here: http://burtleburtle.net/bob/hash/doobs.htmlDi2015NewLine    /// I got this code from here: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/3404715/c-sharp-hashcode-for-array-of-intsDi2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="obj"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public override int GetHashCode(PossibleGrouping obj) {Di2015NewLine        var array = obj.FriendsInGroup;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        int hc = obj.FriendsInGroup.Length;Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < array.Length; ++i) {Di2015NewLine            hc = unchecked(hc*314159 + array[i]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return hc;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
10027211Di2015UniqueSeparatorPossibleGroupingComparer

10033864Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class Graph<T>Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public Dictionary<T, HashSet<T>> nodesNeighbors;Di2015NewLine    public IEnumerable<T> NodesDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        get { return nodesNeighbors.Keys; }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public Graph()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        this.nodesNeighbors = new Dictionary<T, HashSet<T>>();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public void AddNode(T node)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        this.nodesNeighbors.Add(node, new HashSet<T>());Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public void AddNodes(IEnumerable<T> nodes)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        foreach (var n in nodes)Di2015NewLine            this.AddNode(n);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public void AddArc(T from, T to)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        this.nodesNeighbors[from].Add(to);Di2015NewLine        this.nodesNeighbors[to].Add(from);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public bool ContainsNode(T node)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return this.nodesNeighbors.ContainsKey(node);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public IEnumerable<T> GetNeighbors(T node)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return nodesNeighbors[node];Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public IEnumerable<T> DepthFirstSearch(T nodeStart)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var stack = new Stack<T>();Di2015NewLine        var visitedNodes = new HashSet<T>();Di2015NewLine        stack.Push(nodeStart);Di2015NewLine        while (stack.Count > 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            var curr = stack.Pop();Di2015NewLine            if (!visitedNodes.Contains(curr))Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                visitedNodes.Add(curr);Di2015NewLine                yield return curr;Di2015NewLine                foreach (var next in this.GetNeighbors(curr))Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    if (!visitedNodes.Contains(next))Di2015NewLine                        stack.Push(next);Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public Graph<T> GetSubGraph(IEnumerable<T> nodes)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Graph<T> g = new Graph<T>();Di2015NewLine        g.AddNodes(nodes);Di2015NewLine        foreach (var n in g.Nodes.ToList())Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            foreach (var neigh in this.GetNeighbors(n))Di2015NewLine                g.AddArc(n, neigh);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return g;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public IEnumerable<Graph<T>> GetConnectedComponents()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var visitedNodes = new HashSet<T>();Di2015NewLine        var components = new List<Graph<T>>();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        foreach (var node in this.Nodes)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (!visitedNodes.Contains(node))Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                var subGraph = GetSubGraph(this.DepthFirstSearch(node));Di2015NewLine                components.Add(subGraph);Di2015NewLine                visitedNodes.UnionWith(subGraph.Nodes);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return components;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10041736Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate int firstX, firstY;//store coordinates of first clickDi2015NewLineprivate bool firstClick = true;Di2015NewLineprivate void panel1_MouseClick(object sender, MouseEventArgs e)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (firstClick)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        firstX = e.X;Di2015NewLine        firstY = e.Y;Di2015NewLine        firstClick = false;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    elseDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Line l = new Line();Di2015NewLine        l.LineBres(firstX, firstY, e.X, e.Y, panel1.CreateGraphics());Di2015NewLine        firstClick = true;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic class LineDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    private Color grad1 = Color.FromArgb(165, 194, 245);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public void LineBres(int x0, int y0, int xEnd, int yEnd, Graphics e)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int dx = xEnd - x0;Di2015NewLine        int dy = yEnd = y0;Di2015NewLine        int p = 2*dy - dx;Di2015NewLine        int twoDy = 2*dy;Di2015NewLine        int twoDyMinusDx = 2*(dy - dx);Di2015NewLine        int x, y;Di2015NewLine        if (x0 > xEnd)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            x = xEnd;Di2015NewLine            y = yEnd;Di2015NewLine            xEnd = x0;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            x = x0;Di2015NewLine            y = y0;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        e.FillRectangle(new SolidBrush(grad1), x, y, 1, 1);Di2015NewLine        while (x < xEnd)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            x++;Di2015NewLine            if (p < 0)Di2015NewLine                p += twoDy;Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                y++;Di2015NewLine                p += twoDyMinusDx;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            e.FillRectangle(new SolidBrush(grad1), x, y, 1, 1);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10041855Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static class UsefulExtensionsDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public static bool LooseContains(this IEnumerable<string> list, string word,int distance)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        foreach (var s in list)Di2015NewLine            if (s.LevenshteinDistance(word) <= distance) return true;Di2015NewLine        return false;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //Di2015NewLine    //http://www.merriampark.com/ldcsharp.htmDi2015NewLine    //Di2015NewLine    public static int LevenshteinDistance(this string s, string t)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int n = s.Length;Di2015NewLine        int m = t.Length;Di2015NewLine        int[,] d = new int[n + 1, m + 1];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Step 1Di2015NewLine        if (n == 0)Di2015NewLine            return m;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (m == 0)Di2015NewLine            return n;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Step 2Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i <= n; d[i, 0] = i++){}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        for (int j = 0; j <= m; d[0, j] = j++){}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Step 3Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            //Step 4Di2015NewLine            for (int j = 1; j <= m; j++)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                // Step 5Di2015NewLine                int cost = (char.ToUpperInvariant(t[j - 1]) == char.ToUpperInvariant(s[i - 1])) ? 0 : 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                // Step 6Di2015NewLine                d[i, j] = Math.Min(Di2015NewLine                    Math.Min(d[i - 1, j] + 1, d[i, j - 1] + 1),Di2015NewLine                    d[i - 1, j - 1] + cost);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        // Step 7Di2015NewLine        return d[n, m];Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10045428Di2015UniqueSeparator[Authorize]Di2015NewLinepublic ActionResult AddToCart(int productId, int quantity)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    //If the cart cookie doesn't exist, create it.Di2015NewLine    if (Request.Cookies["cart"] == null)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Response.Cookies.Add(new HttpCookie("cart"));Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //Helper method here.Di2015NewLine    var values = GenerateNameValueCollection(Request.Cookies["cart"], productId, quantity);Di2015NewLine    Response.Cookies["cart"].Values.Add(values);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return RedirectToAction("Index");Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
10045428Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate NameValueCollection GenerateNameValueCollection(HttpCookie cookie, int productId, int quantity)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var collection = new NameValueCollection();Di2015NewLine    foreach (var value in cookie.Values)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        //If the current element isn't the first empty element.Di2015NewLine        if (value != null)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            collection.Add(value.ToString(), cookie.Values[value.ToString()]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //Does this product exist in the cookie?Di2015NewLine    if (cookie.Values[productId.ToString()] != null)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        collection.Remove(productId.ToString());Di2015NewLine        //Get current count of item in cart.Di2015NewLine        int tmpAmount = Convert.ToInt32(cookie.Values[productId.ToString()]);Di2015NewLine        int total = tmpAmount + quantity;Di2015NewLine        collection.Add(productId.ToString(), total.ToString());Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    else //It doesn't exist, so add it.Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        collection.Add(productId.ToString(), quantity.ToString());Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (!collection.HasKeys())Di2015NewLine        collection.Add(productId.ToString(), quantity.ToString());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return collection;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10052736Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static string Generator (Filter filters) {Di2015NewLine    var sb = new StringBuilder ();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (filters.groups != null && filters.groups.Count > 0)Di2015NewLine        sb.Append (" (");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    bool firstRule = true;Di2015NewLine    if (filters.rules != null) {Di2015NewLine        foreach (var rule in filters.rules) {Di2015NewLine            if (!firstRule)Di2015NewLine                sb.Append (filters.groupOp);Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine                firstRule = false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            sb.AppendFormat (FormatMapping[(int)rule.op], rule.field, rule.data);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (filters.groups != null && filters.groups.Count > 0) {Di2015NewLine        sb.Append (") ");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        foreach (var filter in filters.groups) {Di2015NewLine            if (sb.Length != 0)Di2015NewLine                sb.Append (filter.groupOp);Di2015NewLine            sb.Append (" (");Di2015NewLine            sb.Append (Generator (filter));Di2015NewLine            sb.Append (") ");Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return sb.ToString ();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10052736Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class Filter {Di2015NewLine    public GroupOp groupOp { get; set; }Di2015NewLine    public List<Rule> rules { get; set; }Di2015NewLine    public List<Filter> groups { get; set; }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic class Rule {Di2015NewLine    public string field { get; set; }Di2015NewLine    public Operations op { get; set; }Di2015NewLine    public string data { get; set; }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic enum GroupOp {Di2015NewLine    AND,Di2015NewLine    ORDi2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic enum Operations {Di2015NewLine    eq, // "equal"Di2015NewLine    ne, // "not equal"Di2015NewLine    lt, // "less"Di2015NewLine    le, // "less or equal"Di2015NewLine    gt, // "greater"Di2015NewLine    ge, // "greater or equal"Di2015NewLine    bw, // "begins with"Di2015NewLine    bn, // "does not begin with"Di2015NewLine    //in, // "in"Di2015NewLine    //ni, // "not in"Di2015NewLine    ew, // "ends with"Di2015NewLine    en, // "does not end with"Di2015NewLine    cn, // "contains"Di2015NewLine    nc  // "does not contain"Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic static class WhereClauseGenerator {Di2015NewLine    private static readonly string[] FormatMapping = {Di2015NewLine        "({0} = '{1}')",               // "eq" - equalDi2015NewLine        "({0} <> {1})",                // "ne" - not equalDi2015NewLine        "({0} < {1})",                 // "lt" - less thanDi2015NewLine        "({0} <= {1})",                // "le" - less than or equal toDi2015NewLine        "({0} > {1})",                 // "gt" - greater thanDi2015NewLine        "({0} >= {1})",                // "ge" - greater than or equal toDi2015NewLine        "({0} LIKE '{1}%')",           // "bw" - begins withDi2015NewLine        "({0} NOT LIKE '{1}%')",       // "bn" - does not begin withDi2015NewLine        "({0} LIKE '%{1}')",           // "ew" - ends withDi2015NewLine        "({0} NOT LIKE '%{1}')",       // "en" - does not end withDi2015NewLine        "({0} LIKE '%{1}%')",          // "cn" - containsDi2015NewLine        "({0} NOT LIKE '%{1}%')"       // "nc" - does not containDi2015NewLine    };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static StringBuilder ParseRule(ICollection<Rule> rules, GroupOp groupOp) {Di2015NewLine        if (rules == null || rules.Count == 0)Di2015NewLine            return null;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var sb = new StringBuilder ();Di2015NewLine        bool firstRule = true;Di2015NewLine        foreach (var rule in rules) {Di2015NewLine            if (!firstRule)Di2015NewLine                // skip groupOp before the first ruleDi2015NewLine                sb.Append (groupOp);Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine                firstRule = false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            sb.AppendFormat (FormatMapping[(int)rule.op], rule.field, rule.data);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return sb.Length > 0 ? sb : null;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static void AppendWithBrackets (StringBuilder dest, StringBuilder src) {Di2015NewLine        if (src == null || src.Length == 0)Di2015NewLine            return;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (src.Length > 2 && src[0] != '(' && src[src.Length - 1] != ')') {Di2015NewLine            dest.Append ('(');Di2015NewLine            dest.Append (src);Di2015NewLine            dest.Append (')');Di2015NewLine        } else {Di2015NewLine            // verify that no other '(' and ')' exist in the b. so thatDi2015NewLine            // we have no case like src = "(x < 0) OR (y > 0)"Di2015NewLine            for (int i = 1; i < src.Length - 1; i++) {Di2015NewLine                if (src[i] == '(' || src[i] == ')') {Di2015NewLine                    dest.Append ('(');Di2015NewLine                    dest.Append (src);Di2015NewLine                    dest.Append (')');Di2015NewLine                    return;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            dest.Append (src);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static StringBuilder ParseFilter(ICollection<Filter> groups, GroupOp groupOp) {Di2015NewLine        if (groups == null || groups.Count == 0)Di2015NewLine            return null;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var sb = new StringBuilder ();Di2015NewLine        bool firstGroup = true;Di2015NewLine        foreach (var group in groups) {Di2015NewLine            var sbGroup = ParseFilter(group);Di2015NewLine            if (sbGroup == null || sbGroup.Length == 0)Di2015NewLine                continue;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            if (!firstGroup)Di2015NewLine                // skip groupOp before the first groupDi2015NewLine                sb.Append (groupOp);Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine                firstGroup = false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            sb.EnsureCapacity (sb.Length + sbGroup.Length + 2);Di2015NewLine            AppendWithBrackets (sb, sbGroup);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return sb;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static StringBuilder ParseFilter(Filter filters) {Di2015NewLine        var parsedRules = ParseRule (filters.rules, filters.groupOp);Di2015NewLine        var parsedGroups = ParseFilter (filters.groups, filters.groupOp);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (parsedRules != null && parsedRules.Length > 0) {Di2015NewLine            if (parsedGroups != null && parsedGroups.Length > 0) {Di2015NewLine                var groupOpStr = filters.groupOp.ToString();Di2015NewLine                var sb = new StringBuilder (parsedRules.Length + parsedGroups.Length + groupOpStr.Length + 4);Di2015NewLine                AppendWithBrackets (sb, parsedRules);Di2015NewLine                sb.Append (groupOpStr);Di2015NewLine                AppendWithBrackets (sb, parsedGroups);Di2015NewLine                return sb;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            return parsedRules;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return parsedGroups;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10059483Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate readonly Stopwatch watch;Di2015NewLineprivate readonly long[,] average;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic .ctor() {Di2015NewLine    // use 10 measure points, for a larger or smaller average, adjust the 10Di2015NewLine    average = new long[10, 2];Di2015NewLine    watch = Stopwatch.StartNew();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic long BytesTransferred {Di2015NewLine    set {Di2015NewLine        for (int i = average.GetLength(0) - 1; i > 0; --i) {Di2015NewLine            average[i, 0] = average[i - 1, 0];Di2015NewLine            average[i, 1] = average[i - 1, 1];Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        average[0, 0] = sent = value;Di2015NewLine        average[0, 1] = watch.ElapsedMilliseconds;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic long TransferRate {Di2015NewLine    get {Di2015NewLine        int l = average.GetLength(0) - 1;Di2015NewLine        double bytes = average[0, 0] - average[l, 0];Di2015NewLine        double seconds = (average[0, 1] - average[l, 1]) / 1000d;Di2015NewLine        return (long)(bytes / seconds);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10106800Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic enum JwtHashAlgorithmDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    RS256,Di2015NewLine    HS384,Di2015NewLine    HS512Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic class JsonWebTokenDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    private static Dictionary<JwtHashAlgorithm, Func<byte[], byte[], byte[]>> HashAlgorithms;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static JsonWebToken()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        HashAlgorithms = new Dictionary<JwtHashAlgorithm, Func<byte[], byte[], byte[]>>Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                { JwtHashAlgorithm.RS256, (key, value) => { using (var sha = new HMACSHA256(key)) { return sha.ComputeHash(value); } } },Di2015NewLine                { JwtHashAlgorithm.HS384, (key, value) => { using (var sha = new HMACSHA384(key)) { return sha.ComputeHash(value); } } },Di2015NewLine                { JwtHashAlgorithm.HS512, (key, value) => { using (var sha = new HMACSHA512(key)) { return sha.ComputeHash(value); } } }Di2015NewLine            };Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static string Encode(object payload, string key, JwtHashAlgorithm algorithm)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return Encode(payload, Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(key), algorithm);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static string Encode(object payload, byte[] keyBytes, JwtHashAlgorithm algorithm)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var segments = new List<string>();Di2015NewLine        var header = new { alg = algorithm.ToString(), typ = "JWT" };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        byte[] headerBytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(JsonConvert.SerializeObject(header, Formatting.None));Di2015NewLine        byte[] payloadBytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(JsonConvert.SerializeObject(payload, Formatting.None));Di2015NewLine        //byte[] payloadBytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(@"{"iss":"761326798069-r5mljlln1rd4lrbhg75efgigp36m78j5@developer.gserviceaccount.com","scope":"https://www.googleapis.com/auth/prediction","aud":"https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/token","exp":1328554385,"iat":1328550785}");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        segments.Add(Base64UrlEncode(headerBytes));Di2015NewLine        segments.Add(Base64UrlEncode(payloadBytes));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var stringToSign = string.Join(".", segments.ToArray());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var bytesToSign = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(stringToSign);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        byte[] signature = HashAlgorithms[algorithm](keyBytes, bytesToSign);Di2015NewLine        segments.Add(Base64UrlEncode(signature));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return string.Join(".", segments.ToArray());Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static string Decode(string token, string key)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return Decode(token, key, true);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static string Decode(string token, string key, bool verify)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var parts = token.Split('.');Di2015NewLine        var header = parts[0];Di2015NewLine        var payload = parts[1];Di2015NewLine        byte[] crypto = Base64UrlDecode(parts[2]);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var headerJson = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(Base64UrlDecode(header));Di2015NewLine        var headerData = JObject.Parse(headerJson);Di2015NewLine        var payloadJson = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(Base64UrlDecode(payload));Di2015NewLine        var payloadData = JObject.Parse(payloadJson);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (verify)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            var bytesToSign = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(string.Concat(header, ".", payload));Di2015NewLine            var keyBytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(key);Di2015NewLine            var algorithm = (string)headerData["alg"];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            var signature = HashAlgorithms[GetHashAlgorithm(algorithm)](keyBytes, bytesToSign);Di2015NewLine            var decodedCrypto = Convert.ToBase64String(crypto);Di2015NewLine            var decodedSignature = Convert.ToBase64String(signature);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            if (decodedCrypto != decodedSignature)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                throw new ApplicationException(string.Format("Invalid signature. Expected {0} got {1}", decodedCrypto, decodedSignature));Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return payloadData.ToString();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static JwtHashAlgorithm GetHashAlgorithm(string algorithm)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        switch (algorithm)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            case "RS256": return JwtHashAlgorithm.RS256;Di2015NewLine            case "HS384": return JwtHashAlgorithm.HS384;Di2015NewLine            case "HS512": return JwtHashAlgorithm.HS512;Di2015NewLine            default: throw new InvalidOperationException("Algorithm not supported.");Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // from JWT specDi2015NewLine    private static string Base64UrlEncode(byte[] input)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var output = Convert.ToBase64String(input);Di2015NewLine        output = output.Split('=')[0]; // Remove any trailing '='sDi2015NewLine        output = output.Replace('+', '-'); // 62nd char of encodingDi2015NewLine        output = output.Replace('/', '_'); // 63rd char of encodingDi2015NewLine        return output;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // from JWT specDi2015NewLine    private static byte[] Base64UrlDecode(string input)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var output = input;Di2015NewLine        output = output.Replace('-', '+'); // 62nd char of encodingDi2015NewLine        output = output.Replace('_', '/'); // 63rd char of encodingDi2015NewLine        switch (output.Length % 4) // Pad with trailing '='sDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            case 0: break; // No pad chars in this caseDi2015NewLine            case 2: output += "=="; break; // Two pad charsDi2015NewLine            case 3: output += "="; break; // One pad charDi2015NewLine            default: throw new System.Exception("Illegal base64url string!");Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        var converted = Convert.FromBase64String(output); // Standard base64 decoderDi2015NewLine        return converted;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
10106800Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class GoogleJsonWebTokenDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public static string Encode(string email, string certificateFilePath)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var utc0 = new DateTime(1970,1,1,0,0,0,0, DateTimeKind.Utc);Di2015NewLine        var issueTime = DateTime.Now;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var iat = (int)issueTime.Subtract(utc0).TotalSeconds;Di2015NewLine        var exp = (int)issueTime.AddMinutes(55).Subtract(utc0).TotalSeconds; // Expiration time is up to 1 hour, but lets play on safe sideDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var payload = newDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            iss = email,Di2015NewLine            scope = "https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gan.readonly",Di2015NewLine            aud = "https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/token",Di2015NewLine            exp = exp,Di2015NewLine            iat = iatDi2015NewLine        };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var certificate = new X509Certificate2(certificateFilePath, "notasecret");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var privateKey = certificate.Export(X509ContentType.Cert);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return JsonWebToken.Encode(payload, privateKey, JwtHashAlgorithm.RS256);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10125247Di2015UniqueSeparatorprotected int GetIndexedPixel(int x, int y, BitmapData bmd)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var index = y * bmd.Stride + (x >> 3);Di2015NewLine    var p = Marshal.ReadByte(bmd.Scan0, index);Di2015NewLine    var mask = (byte)(0x80 >> (x & 0x7));Di2015NewLine    return p &= mask;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprotected void SetIndexedPixel(int x, int y, BitmapData bmd, bool pixel)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    int index = y * bmd.Stride + (x >> 3);Di2015NewLine    byte p = Marshal.ReadByte(bmd.Scan0, index);Di2015NewLine    byte mask = (byte)(0x80 >> (x & 0x7));Di2015NewLine    if (pixel)Di2015NewLine        p &= (byte)(mask ^ 0xff);Di2015NewLine    elseDi2015NewLine        p |= mask;Di2015NewLine    Marshal.WriteByte(bmd.Scan0, index, p);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic DocAppImage CutToNew(int left, int top, int width, int height, int pageWidth, int pageHeight)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var destBmp = new Bitmap(pageWidth, pageHeight, BitmapImage.PixelFormat);Di2015NewLine    var pageRect = new Rectangle(0, 0, pageWidth, pageHeight);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    var pageData = destBmp.LockBits(pageRect, ImageLockMode.WriteOnly, BitmapImage.PixelFormat);Di2015NewLine    var croppedRect = new Rectangle(left, top, width, height);Di2015NewLine    var croppedSource = BitmapImage.LockBits(croppedRect, ImageLockMode.ReadWrite, BitmapImage.PixelFormat);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    for (var y = 0; y < pageHeight; y++)Di2015NewLine        for (var x = 0; x < pageWidth; x++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (y >= top && y <= top + height && x >= left && x <= width + left)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                SetIndexedPixel(x, y, pageData,Di2015NewLine                                GetIndexedPixel(x - left, y - top, croppedSource) == 0 ? true : false);Di2015NewLine                SetIndexedPixel(x - left, y - top, croppedSource, false); //Blank area in originalDi2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine                SetIndexedPixel(x, y, pageData, false);  //Fill the remainder of the page with white.Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    destBmp.UnlockBits(pageData);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    var retVal = new DocAppImage { BitmapImage = destBmp };Di2015NewLine    destBmp.Dispose();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    BitmapImage.UnlockBits(croppedSource);Di2015NewLine    SaveBitmapToFileImage(BitmapImage);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return retVal;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

0x00000002,Di2015NewLine        LOAD_LIBRARY_AS_DATAFILE_EXCLUSIVE = 0x00000040,Di2015NewLine        LOAD_LIBRARY_AS_IMAGE_RESOURCE = 0x00000020,Di2015NewLine        LOAD_WITH_ALTERED_SEARCH_PATH = 0x00000008Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public DLLHelper(string dllpath)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        PESizeOfImage = GetDllSizeInMemory(dllpath);Di2015NewLine        dllInMemory = GetDLLCopy(dllpath, PESizeOfImage);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VA_p_PE = 0x3C;Di2015NewLine        VA_PE = Get4ByteFromLocation(VA_p_PE, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private byte[] GetDLLCopy(string dllpath, uint PESizeOfImage)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        IntPtr libPtr = LoadLibraryEx(dllpath, IntPtr.Zero, LoadLibraryFlags.DONT_RESOLVE_DLL_REFERENCES);Di2015NewLine        byte[] dllInMemory = new byte[PESizeOfImage];Di2015NewLine        Marshal.Copy(libPtr, dllInMemory, 0, (int)PESizeOfImage);Di2015NewLine        FreeLibrary(libPtr);Di2015NewLine        return dllInMemory;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private UInt32 GetDllSizeInMemory(string dllpath)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        byte[] dllpreload = File.ReadAllBytes(dllpath);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 pp_PE = 0x3C;Di2015NewLine        UInt32 p_PE = Get4ByteFromLocation(pp_PE, dllpreload);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 p_PEOPTIONALHEADER = p_PE + 0x18;Di2015NewLine        UInt32 p_PESizeOfImage = p_PEOPTIONALHEADER + 0x38;Di2015NewLine        return Get4ByteFromLocation(p_PESizeOfImage, dllpreload);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public void DumpToFile(String filename)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        File.WriteAllBytes(filename, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public string GetDLLName()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VAExport = GetVAExport(VA_PE, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VAName = GetVAName(VAExport, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        String Name = GetString(VAName, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        return Name;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public List<String> GetFunctionNames()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        List<String> fkts = new List<String>();Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VAExport = GetVAExport(VA_PE, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VA_p_firstFKT = GetVA_p_firstFKT(VAExport, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VA_p_lastFKT = GetVA_p_lastFKT(VAExport, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        for (UInt32 VA_p_fkt = VA_p_firstFKT; VA_p_fkt <= VA_p_lastFKT; VA_p_fkt += sizeof(UInt32))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            UInt32 VA_fkt = Get4ByteFromLocation(VA_p_fkt, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine            fkts.Add(GetString(VA_fkt, dllInMemory));Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return fkts;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private UInt32 GetVA_p_lastFKT(UInt32 VAExport, byte[] dllInMemory)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        UInt32 first = GetVA_p_firstFKT(VAExport, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 count = GetfktCount(VAExport, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine        UInt32 last = first + (count - 1) * sizeof(UInt32);Di2015NewLine        return last;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private UInt32 GetfktCount(UInt32 VAExport, byte[] dllInMemory)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        UInt32 RVA_Count = 0x14;Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VA_Count = VAExport + RVA_Count;Di2015NewLine        return Get4ByteFromLocation(VA_Count, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private UInt32 GetVA_p_firstFKT(UInt32 VAExport, byte[] dllInMemory)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        UInt32 RVA_p_FIRST = 0x20;Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VA_p_FIRST = VAExport + RVA_p_FIRST;Di2015NewLine        return Get4ByteFromLocation(VA_p_FIRST, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private UInt32 GetVAName(UInt32 VAExport, byte[] dllInMemory)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        UInt32 private UInt32 GetVAExport(UInt32 VAPE, byte[] dllInMemory)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        UInt32 RVA_p_EXPORT = 0x78;Di2015NewLine        UInt32 VA_p_EXPORT = VAPE + RVA_p_EXPORT;Di2015NewLine        return Get4ByteFromLocation(VA_p_EXPORT, dllInMemory);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   string GetString(UInt32 location, byte[] dll)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int length = 0;Di2015NewLine        while (dll[location + length] != 0x00)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            length++;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        if (location > int.MaxValue) throw new Exception("uncastable");Di2015NewLine        return Encoding.UTF8.GetString(dll, (int)location, length);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   private UInt32 Get4ByteFromLocation(UInt32 location, byte[] dll)Di2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine       if (!(BitConverter.IsLittleEndian))Di2015NewLine       {Di2015NewLine           byte[] partial = GetByteSubset(4, location, dll);Di2015NewLine           Array.Reverse(partial);Di2015NewLine           return BitConverter.ToUInt32(partial, 0);Di2015NewLine       }Di2015NewLine       return BitConverter.ToUInt32(dll, (int)location);Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   private byte[] GetByteSubset(int size, UInt32 location, byte[] dll)Di2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine       byte[] val = new byte[size];Di2015NewLine       for (int i = 0; i < size; i++)Di2015NewLine       {Di2015NewLine           val[i] = dll[location + i];Di2015NewLine       }Di2015NewLine       return val;Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10148114Di2015UniqueSeparatorclass ProgramDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Format a value using engineering notation.Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <example>Di2015NewLine    ///     Format("S4",-12345678.9) = "-12.34e-6"Di2015NewLine    ///     with 4 significant digitsDi2015NewLine    /// </example>Di2015NewLine    /// <arg name="format">The format specifier</arg>Di2015NewLine    /// <arg name="value">The value</arg>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns>A string representing the value formatted according to the format specifier</returns>Di2015NewLine    public static string Format(string format, double value)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        if(format.StartsWith("S"))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            string dg=format.Substring(1);Di2015NewLine            int significant_digits;Di2015NewLine            int.TryParse(dg, out significant_digits);Di2015NewLine            if(significant_digits==0) significant_digits=4;Di2015NewLine            int sign;Di2015NewLine            double amt;Di2015NewLine            int exponent;Di2015NewLine            SplitEngineeringParts(value, out sign, out amt, out exponent);Di2015NewLine            return ComposeEngrFormat(significant_digits, sign, amt, exponent);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return value.ToString(format);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    static void SplitEngineeringParts(double value,Di2015NewLine                out int sign,Di2015NewLine                out double new_value,Di2015NewLine                out int exponent)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        sign=Math.Sign(value);Di2015NewLine        value=Math.Abs(value);Di2015NewLine        if(value>0.0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if(value>1.0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                exponent=(int)(Math.Floor(Math.Log10(value)/3.0)*3.0);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                exponent=(int)(Math.Ceiling(Math.Log10(value)/3.0)*3.0);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            exponent=0;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        new_value=value*Math.Pow(10.0, -exponent);Di2015NewLine        if(new_value>=1e3)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            new_value/=1e3;Di2015NewLine            exponent+=3;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        if(new_value<=1e-3&&new_value>0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            new_value*=1e3;Di2015NewLine            exponent-=3;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    static string ComposeEngrFormat(int significant_digits, int sign, double v, int exponent)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int expsign=Math.Sign(exponent);Di2015NewLine        exponent=Math.Abs(exponent);Di2015NewLine        int digits=v>0?(int)Math.Log10(v)+1:0;Di2015NewLine        int decimals=Math.Max(significant_digits-digits, 0);Di2015NewLine        double round=Math.Pow(10, -decimals);Di2015NewLine        digits=v>0?(int)Math.Log10(v+0.5*round)+1:0;Di2015NewLine        decimals=Math.Max(significant_digits-digits, 0);Di2015NewLine        string t;Di2015NewLine        string f="0:F";Di2015NewLine        if(exponent==0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            t=string.Format("{"+f+decimals+"}", sign*v);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            t=string.Format("{"+f+decimals+"}e{1}", sign*v, expsign*exponent);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return t;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static void Main(string[] args)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t1.0      = {0}", Format("S3", 1.0));Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t0.1      = {0}", Format("S3", 0.1));Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t0.01     = {0}", Format("S3", 0.01));Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t0.001    = {0}", Format("S3", 0.001));Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t0.0001   = {0}", Format("S3", 0.0001));Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t0.00001  = {0}", Format("S3", 0.00001));Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("\\t0.000001 = {0}", Format("S3", 0.000001));Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10150991Di2015UniqueSeparatorclass ProgramDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    const int Million = 1000 * 1000;Di2015NewLine    static readonly int NumValues = 32 * Million;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static void Main(string[] args)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // Construct a table of integers.Di2015NewLine        // These are random powers of two.Di2015NewLine        // That is 2^N, where N is in the range 0..31.Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("Constructing table");Di2015NewLine        int[] values = new int[NumValues];Di2015NewLine        Random rnd = new Random();Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < NumValues; ++i)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            int pow = rnd.Next(31);Di2015NewLine            values[i] = 1 << pow;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Run each one once to make sure it's JITtedDi2015NewLine        GetLog2_Bithack(values[0]);Di2015NewLine        GetLog2_DeBruijn(values[0]);Di2015NewLine        GetLog2_Switch(values[0]);Di2015NewLine        GetLog2_Naive(values[0]);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Stopwatch sw = new Stopwatch();Di2015NewLine        Console.Write("GetLog2_Naive ... ");Di2015NewLine        sw.Restart();Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < NumValues; ++i)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            GetLog2_Naive(values[i]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        sw.Stop();Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("{0:N0} ms", sw.ElapsedMilliseconds);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Console.Write("GetLog2_Switch ... ");Di2015NewLine        sw.Restart();Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < NumValues; ++i)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            GetLog2_Switch(values[i]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        sw.Stop();Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("{0:N0} ms", sw.ElapsedMilliseconds);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Console.Write("GetLog2_Bithack ... ");Di2015NewLine        sw.Restart();Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < NumValues; ++i)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            GetLog2_Bithack(values[i]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("{0:N0} ms", sw.ElapsedMilliseconds);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Console.Write("GetLog2_DeBruijn ... ");Di2015NewLine        sw.Restart();Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < NumValues; ++i)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            GetLog2_DeBruijn(values[i]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        sw.Stop();Di2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("{0:N0} ms", sw.ElapsedMilliseconds);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Console.ReadLine();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static int GetLog2_Naive(int v)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int r = 0;Di2015NewLine        while ((v = v >> 1) != 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            ++r;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return r;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static readonly int[] MultiplyDeBruijnBitPosition2 = new int[32]Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        0, 1, 28, 2, 29, 14, 24, 3, 30, 22, 20, 15, 25, 17, 4, 8, Di2015NewLine        31, 27, 13, 23, 21, 19, 16, 7, 26, 12, 18, 6, 11, 5, 10, 9Di2015NewLine    };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static int GetLog2_DeBruijn(int v)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return MultiplyDeBruijnBitPosition2[(uint)(v * 0x077CB531U) >> 27];Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static readonly uint[] b = new uint[] { 0xAAAAAAAA, 0xCCCCCCCC, 0xF0F0F0F0, 0xFF00FF00, 0xFFFF0000};Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static int GetLog2_Bithack(int v)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int r = (v & b[0]) == 0 ? 0 : 1;Di2015NewLine        int x = 1 << 4;Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 4; i > 0; i--) // unroll for speed...Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if ((v & b[i]) != 0)Di2015NewLine                r |= x;Di2015NewLine            x >>= 1;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return r;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static int GetLog2_Switch(int v)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        switch (v)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            case 0x00000001: return 0;Di2015NewLine            case 0x00000002: return 1;Di2015NewLine            case 0x00000004: return 2;Di2015NewLine            case 0x00000008: return 3;Di2015NewLine            case 0x00000010: return 10150991Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic int GetLog2_Bithack(int v)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    int r = ((v & 0xAAAAAAAA) != 0) ? 1 : 0;Di2015NewLine    if ((v & 0xFFFF0000) != 0) r |= (1 << 4);Di2015NewLine    if ((v & 0xFF00FF00) != 0) r |= (1 << 3);Di2015NewLine    if ((v & 0xF0F0F0F0) != 0) r |= (1 << 2);Di2015NewLine    if ((v & 0xCCCCCCCC) != 0) r |= (1 << 1);Di2015NewLine    return r;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10153508Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate PointF[] CreateBaseSignal(SignalType signalType)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine  switch (signalType)Di2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine    case SignalType.Sine:Di2015NewLine      const int oversampling = 32;Di2015NewLine      PointF[] signal = new PointF[oversampling];Di2015NewLine      for (int i = 0; i < signal.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine      {Di2015NewLine        signal[i].X = (float) i / oversampling;Di2015NewLine        signal[i].Y = Convert.ToSingle(Math.Sin((double) i / oversampling * 2 * Math.PI));Di2015NewLine      }Di2015NewLine      return signal;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    case SignalType.Square:Di2015NewLine      return new PointF[]Di2015NewLine      {Di2015NewLine        new PointF(0.0f, -1.0f),Di2015NewLine        new PointF(0.5f, -1.0f),Di2015NewLine        new PointF(0.5f, 1.0f),Di2015NewLine        new PointF(1.0f, 1.0f),Di2015NewLine      };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    case SignalType.Triangle:Di2015NewLine      return new PointF[]Di2015NewLine      {Di2015NewLine        new PointF(0.0f, -1.0f),Di2015NewLine        new PointF(0.5f, 1.0f),Di2015NewLine      };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    case SignalType.Sawtooth:Di2015NewLine      return new PointF[]Di2015NewLine      {Di2015NewLine        new PointF(0.0f, -1.0f),Di2015NewLine        new PointF(1.0f, 1.0f),Di2015NewLine      };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    default:Di2015NewLine      throw new ArgumentException("Invalid signal type", "signalType");Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
10153508Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate PointF[] CreateSignal(PointF[] baseSignal, float frequency, float amplitude)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine  PointF[] signal = new PointF[Convert.ToInt32(Math.Ceiling(baseSignal.Length * frequency))];Di2015NewLine  for(int i = 0; i < signal.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine    signal[i].X = baseSignal[i % baseSignal.Length].X / frequency + (i / baseSignal.Length) / frequency;Di2015NewLine    signal[i].Y = baseSignal[i % baseSignal.Length].Y * amplitude;Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine  return signal;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
10153508Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate PointF[] ScaleSignal(PointF[] signal, int width, int height)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine  const float maximumAmplitude = 10.0f;Di2015NewLine  PointF[] scaledSignal = new PointF[signal.Length];Di2015NewLine  for(int i = 0; i < signal.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine    scaledSignal[i].X = signal[i].X * width;Di2015NewLine    scaledSignal[i].Y = signal[i].Y * height / 2 / maximumAmplitude;Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine  return scaledSignal;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
10153508Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate void PlotSignal(PointF[] signal, PictureBox pictureBox)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine  Bitmap bmp = new Bitmap(pictureBox.ClientSize.Width, pictureBox.ClientSize.Height);Di2015NewLine  signal = ScaleSignal(signal, bmp.Width, bmp.Height); // Scale signal to fit imageDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine  using(Graphics gfx = Graphics.FromImage(bmp))Di2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine    gfx.SmoothingMode = SmoothingMode.HighQuality;Di2015NewLine    gfx.TranslateTransform(0, bmp.Height / 2); // Move Y=0 to center of imageDi2015NewLine    gfx.ScaleTransform(1, -1); // Make positive Y axis point upwardDi2015NewLine    gfx.DrawLine(Pens.Black, 0, 0, bmp.Width, 0); // Draw zero axisDi2015NewLine    gfx.DrawLines(Pens.Blue, signal); // Draw signalDi2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine  // Make sure the bitmap is disposed the next time aroundDi2015NewLine  Image old = pictureBox.Image;Di2015NewLine  pictureBox.Image = bmp;Di2015NewLine  if(old != null)Di2015NewLine    old.Dispose();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

10174477Di2015UniqueSeparator      FUNCTION POLY(N,A,X)      ! implicitly real (float) function poly(int n,int a,real x)Di2015NewLine      DIMENSION A(N)            ! shape A as 1d array of n values in this scopeDi2015NewLineC                               ! say nothing (blank comment)Di2015NewLine      POLY    = 0.              ! initialise return variable to float value 0Di2015NewLine      L       = N               ! set L (implicitly integer) to nDi2015NewLine      DO 1 K  = 1,N             ! for(int k=1; k<=n; ++k)Di2015NewLine      POLY    = POLY*X + A(L)   !    update return variableDi2015NewLine1     L       = L-1             !    decrement LDi2015NewLine      RETURN                    ! return current value for polyDi2015NewLine      END Di2015NewLine

Default keysize is 256, so the IV must beDi2015NewLine        // 32 bytes long.  Using a 16 character string here gives us 32 bytes when converted to a byte array.Di2015NewLine        private const string initVector = "tu89geji340t89u2";Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // This constant is used to determine the keysize of the encryption algorithm.Di2015NewLine        private const int keysize = 256;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public static string Encrypt(string plainText, string passPhrase)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            byte[] initVectorBytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(initVector);Di2015NewLine            byte[] plainTextBytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(plainText);Di2015NewLine            PasswordDeriveBytes password = new PasswordDeriveBytes(passPhrase, null);Di2015NewLine            byte[] keyBytes = password.GetBytes(keysize / 8);Di2015NewLine            RijndaelManaged symmetricKey = new RijndaelManaged();Di2015NewLine            symmetricKey.Mode = CipherMode.CBC;Di2015NewLine            ICryptoTransform encryptor = symmetricKey.CreateEncryptor(keyBytes, initVectorBytes);Di2015NewLine            MemoryStream memoryStream = new MemoryStream();Di2015NewLine            CryptoStream cryptoStream = new CryptoStream(memoryStream, encryptor, CryptoStreamMode.Write);Di2015NewLine            cryptoStream.Write(plainTextBytes, 0, plainTextBytes.Length);Di2015NewLine            cryptoStream.FlushFinalBlock();Di2015NewLine            byte[] cipherTextBytes = memoryStream.ToArray();Di2015NewLine            memoryStream.Close();Di2015NewLine            cryptoStream.Close();Di2015NewLine            return Convert.ToBase64String(cipherTextBytes);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public static string Decrypt(string cipherText, password.GetBytes(keysize / 8);Di2015NewLine            RijndaelManaged symmetricKey = new RijndaelManaged();Di2015NewLine            symmetricKey.Mode = CipherMode.CBC;Di2015NewLine            ICryptoTransform decryptor = symmetricKey.CreateDecryptor(keyBytes, initVectorBytes);Di2015NewLine            MemoryStream memoryStream = new MemoryStream(cipherTextBytes);Di2015NewLine            CryptoStream cryptoStream = new CryptoStream(memoryStream, decryptor, CryptoStreamMode.Read);Di2015NewLine            byte[] plainTextBytes = new byte[cipherTextBytes.Length];Di2015NewLine            int decryptedByteCount = cryptoStream.Read(plainTextBytes, 0, plainTextBytes.Length);Di2015NewLine            memoryStream.Close();Di2015NewLine            cryptoStream.Close();Di2015NewLine
